+	/*
+	 * From RZ/V2H HW manual (Rev.1.20) section 9.5.3 Operation,
+	 * (C) After write to D-PHY registers we need to wait for more than 1 x tp
+	 *
+	 * tp = 1 / (PLLREFCLK / PLLCLKSET0R.PLL_P)
+	 * PLLREFCLK = 24MHz
+	 * PLLCLKSET0R.PLL_P = {1, 2, 3, 4}
